      <processinfo id="aspace_ece3e85e9ab30b92cdeb684a14953ad3">
         <head>Processing Information</head>
         <p>Yale University records are arranged and described at the accession level by the creating office. The University Archives creates collection level descriptive records, but typically does no further arrangement and description at the accession level.</p>  
      </processinfo>
      <bioghist id="aspace_2aa321c9af6046c744e30f6b70073c4e">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>The Yale Aviation Club was founded in 1945.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_577cf26d76446555ef0178ef3f1f5535">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of membership lists, correspondence, subject files, reference materials, mailings to members, and other materials documenting the Yale Aviation Club.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_3d152640065d8d8d7d823e5d4fbea963">
